Manchester United are favourites to sign Danny Ings from Burnley in the summer . 
  Ings has scored nine goals in his first season in the Premier League . 
  Liverpool were prepared to exploit a Premier League loophole to guarantee a transfer . 
  Louis van Gaal has held talks with Burnley about a summer deal for Ings . 
  The striker impressed against United at Old Trafford in February . 
 